data.message: Go ahead Em, let the record spin from beginning to end, oh wait im bout to do it again, sorry but im bout to slay him, they call you slim, they call me slend, idk what it is but i tend to spend time on rhymes, idk why but most you rappers today just lie, just be old school and rap about real life, like TQ when he raps about the Westside, then you will see why mr.mathers doesn't even have to try, its just game, not talking about this rap battle but just your name, i think your called something like fake or drake, sorry im bad with names, my mistake but maybe its time for a change, but Em gonna put that name to shame while his goes in the hall of fame, you write it, his comes straight from the brian, sometimes what he says is so insane, he is like a drug he is gonna free pain, after he beats you you're gonna need some and a walking cane, like you've been shot down from a plane, he is gonna burn you like a campfire flame, you raps are repetitive they're all the same, now you're dead but you're the only one to blame
